WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
The S500 Standard is the industry benchmark for water damage restoration.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
It defines the procedures, equipment, and documentation required for professional restoration work.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
RestoreAssist automatically formats all reports to S500 specifications, ensuring compliance with insurer and regulatory requirements.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
Key sections include: scope of work, moisture measurements, drying equipment logs, and verification of dryness.

00:32.000 --> 00:40.000
Understanding S500 gives you credibility with insurers and clients.